healer adept~
The Adept of Kyorlin~
An Adept of Kyorlin stands here helping those new to Amethyst
~
The adept of Kyorlin is a living statue, which is imbued with magical
properties allowing it to cast healing spells.  When in this room, it will
heal you with it's spells.  To speed the healing process, see HELP REST
for information on recovering.
~
