> all_greet_prog 100~
if isimmort($n)
else
if level($n) > 5
look $n
'I'm sorry $n, but you're too high of a level for me to permit you to enter.
'After all, there are real newbies that need to practice and advance.
mpforce $n s
endif
endif
~
> all_greet_prog 100~
if multi($n) > 1
mpechoat 0.$n _red Sorry $n, but you're not allowed on here right now.
mpforce 0.$n quit
endif
~
> act_prog p grovels in the dirt.~
tell $n In case you hadn't noticed, this isn't Realms...
~
> act_prog p grovels in the dirt before you.~
tell $n In case you hadn't noticed, this isn't Realms...
~
