> act_prog p has entered the game.~
if multi($n) > 1
mpechoat 0.$n _red Sorry, but you're not allowed on here right now...
mpat 0.$n mpforce 0.$n quit
else
if level($n)==1
mpat hvak1 mpforce hvak1 ask What new soul has entered the troubled world of Amethyst?
