#ROOMS
#13301
A Forming Planet~
You float high above the world, and are presented with two choices. To 
those most eager to journey onwards, there is an exit below which seems 
to lead down many miles into the heart of a great city. For those less
foolhardy, or that may simply wish a better grasp of the world itself before
truly entering a note is scribed, "&OSay School and you shall enter
it.&w" You are left to do what you feel is best, but if this is your first
time setting foot within the world it is recommended to visit the school 
at least once.
~
0 2105356 0 101
D5
