#13302
Amethyst Mud Academy~
&WHere you may "&OSAY TOWN&W" and be transported to town square at
any time you're in this room.
You are now in the academy, where you will be able to fight in combat
to gain both experience and earn a supply of equipment.
To the east is a room where you may practice skills.  It is recommended
to learn what skills and spells you have available for optimal combat
ability.
To the west is a store that sells a few essential and basic supplies.
To get money for these, either beg or earn money fighting creatures here.
Go north you can proceed to enter the fighting area to hone your
skills and level.
~
