#13304
Preparing for Combat~
&WTo go down below will put you into the actual area of fighting, where
you will be walking in a square area to fight creatures roaming and
waiting in a single spot to attack you.
If you have not done so already, see "&OHELP CONFIG&W" for help on
configuring yourself.  Also see "&OHELP COMBAT&W" for fighting info
like how to initiate battle.  Again, be forewarned that some creatures
WILL ATTACK YOU on sight.  For help on what to do once you have gotten
equipment off a dead enemy, see "&OHELP WEAR&W"
See "&OHELP WIMPY&W" for help on setting a safety zone for you to
automatically flee should you come near death.
~
