#13316
Culdesac~
This is the beginning of the northern side of the simple culdesac of the lower
catacombs, where you can wind around in a constant manner to fight many things
lurking about down here, and gain experience in the process.  It will continue
east for 2 rooms before coming back in a full u-turn across the southern side.
