grate~
It's fairly open and closeable, but looks to be extremely heavy, so you
wouldn't want to try to move it anyways.  There are a lot of deep scratches on
the wall surrounding it, seems someone or something has taken up moving it
around as some kind of hobby, but either way lucky for you it's cracked open
enough to squeeze through without too much trouble, thought no telling why
anyone would want to, it's dark in there.
~
