#13321
Academy store~
&WThis is the academy store.  The owner is here to sell you some minor goods
which are essential to you, such as food and drink so you don't starve
or dehydrate inside the academy.  To learn to use shops, type "&OHELP BUY&W"
If you need a player's guide for whatever reason, simply type "&OSAY I
NEED A BOOK&W" and Eisen will be more then happy to give you one, free
of charge.
~
